   "cell_type": "markdown",

   "source": [
    "## Matplotlib+Seaborn\n",
    "\n",
    "Matplotlib 是 Python 中一种第三方可视化绘图库，Matplotlib是 MATLAB+Plot+Library 的缩写，其绘图风格与 MATLAB 类似。Seaborn 在 Matplotlib 的基础上，为图形样式和颜色设置提供了现代化的设置为常用的统计图形定义了许多简单的高级函数，并与 Pandas.DataFrame 的功能有机结合。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 版本"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:42.972525Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:42.165814Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "('3.0.3', '0.9.0')"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 1,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib\n",
    "import seaborn\n",
    "\n",
    "matplotlib.__version__,seaborn.__version__"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 别名\n",
    "\n",
    "遵循传统，使用别名`mpl`导入 Matplotlib；`sns`导入 Seaborn；`plt`导入 matplotlib.pyplot，这是 matplotlib 中最常用的绘图接口。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:42.983021Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:42.975444Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib as mpl\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "sns.set()\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "加入`%matplotlib inline`会在 Notebook 中启动静态图形；加入`sns.set()`使图像拥有更好的视觉效果。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Figure\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Matplotlib 中，图像为一个 `figure` 对象，在 `Figure` 对象中可以包含一个或多个 `Axes` 对象。每个`Axes(ax)` 对象都是一个拥有自己坐标系统的绘图区域，所属关系如下图所示：\n",
    "\n",
    "![Figure(图片来自 Matplotlib 官网)](../image/figure.png)\n",
    "\n",
    "其中，`Title` 为图像标题，`Axis` 为坐标轴, `Label` 为坐标轴标注，`Tick` 为刻度线，`Tick Label` 为刻度注释。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.252651Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:42.985277Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# 生成数据\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "x = np.linspace(1,10,50)\n",
    "y = np.sin(x)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建一个空的 figure 对象\n",
    "fig = plt.figure() \n",
    "\n",
    "# 添加标签\n",
    "plt.xlabel('x')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('y')\n",
    "plt.title('y = sin(x)')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘图\n",
    "plt.plot(x, y)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 图像导出\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Matplotlib 中，可以通过 `savefig()` 命令将图像保存为文件："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.326187Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.256425Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig.savefig('sin(x).png')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T07:02:24.776051Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T07:02:24.759322Z"
    }
   },
   "source": [
    "在 Notebook 中， 可以通过 `IPython.display.Image` 命令导入图像："
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.344137Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.332578Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<IPython.core.display.Image object>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    " from IPython.display import Image\n",
    "Image('sin(x).png')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

    "\n",

    "\n",

    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:43.612626Z",

    }

   "outputs": [

     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "[<matplotlib.lines.Line2D at 0x7f1e8bc74240>]"

     "metadata": {},

     "output_type": "display_data"
    }

   "source": [

    "y = np.sin(x)\n",
    "plt.plot(x,y)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

   "execution_count": 7,

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "### Seaborn 高级方法\n",
    "\n",
    "Seaborn 提供了许多高级函数，便于进行数据分析工作。\n",
    "\n",
    "#### sns.pairplot()\n",
    "\n",
    "通过 `sns.pairplot()` 方法，能绘制出数据集中的成对关系。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:46.273273Z",
     "start_time": "2019-05-22T08:15:44.100632Z"
    }
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<seaborn.axisgrid.PairGrid at 0x7f1e8bb992b0>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 10,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 720x720 with 20 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# 导入 Iris 数据集\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "iris = pd.read_csv('./data/iris.csv')\n",
    "sns.pairplot(iris)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
